rComments: Really caring Prof as she explains concepts really well during lectures. We have to be fully switched on during her class or else you might miss some things that she teaches. Very approachable even after class and sometimes cracks some jokes.

You can tell she really cares about her students doing their best. Her lectures are lots of examples (sometimes too basic of problems) that really help you understand the concepts and how to solve problems. Easy to contact her for help in office hours. Learns everyones names even if you have never directly interacted with her!
